name: live in a jar 2/20
description:
Here, where I live, I often hear people are saying that if you hit someone in the jar, she will do anything that she wants anyway...
For this collection I'm inspired by this story, In fact, for me, this collection is the story of women and girls who have been restricted by those close to them like family, but continue to live and do what they love, and they create their world beautifully even inside these jars.
